node.accessibility_caption: Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 12, 2021. May be a meme of 2 people and text that says 'When I tell my friends I broke up with that person they never liked Tequila!'.

node.text: You were perfect together. What? Really? 🤣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'POST THE THEFOUR WORDS EVERY GIRL WANTS WHISPERED IN HER EAR'.

Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Know the difference between ppl who want to check up on you and people who want to know if they still have access to you'.

Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'For the husband who told his wife I love you' one last time before his plane went down. For the wife who stopped in the stairs to call her husband to say will love you forever' For the mothers & fathers who kissed their kids goodbye the morning they died. For the policemen who rushed in with the firemen to help others only to die themselves. Today, tomorrow, ten years from now- we will remember 9/11.'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A year from now, everything you're stressing about won't mean shit.'.

Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I pray that September, October, November, & December are all months full of growth blessings, productivity, new doors open & opportunities.'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'No one has seen you look worse worse than the gas station closest to your house.'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1 year in jail, or marry your ex?'.

Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'If a guy doesn't text you back, he's probably reading the bible or volunteering at an animal shelter. Men don't cheat, idk who lied to y'all'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 03, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'After gossiping about me, please pray for me. I want to be PERFECT like you.'.

Photo by DAILY DOSE in San Diego, California. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Don't look for pretty face, it will turn old one day. Don't look for soft skin, it will wrinkle one day. But look for a loyal heart, that will miss you everyday and love you forever.'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I have a sad story too. No one cares. Work harder.'.
